# CODEOWNERS — meu-chat-local
#
# Derivado da Matriz RACI documentada no README.md (secao "Governanca de PR").
# Legenda de times:
#   @meu-chat-local/backend     — Responsible por logica de negocio e rotas HTTP
#   @meu-chat-local/platform    — Accountable por infra local-first (db, queue, llm, fs)
#   @meu-chat-local/frontend    — Responsible por UX, SPA e consumo de API
#   @meu-chat-local/governance  — Accountable por compliance, RBAC, auditoria e aprovacoes
#
# Regra de precedencia: a ultima linha que der match em um caminho vence.
# Referencia: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ── Fallback global ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Qualquer arquivo nao coberto por uma regra especifica exige revisao de backend + platform
*                                           @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/platform

# ── Logica de negocio (modules) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# RACI: Backend R/A | Platform C | Frontend C | Governance I
modules/                                    @meu-chat-local/backend

# Modulos sensiveis a compliance requerem revisao adicional de governance
modules/approvals/                          @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance
modules/audit/                              @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance
modules/users/                              @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance

# ── Infraestrutura local-first (platform) ───────────────────────────────────
# RACI: Platform R/A | Backend C | Governance C
platform/                                   @meu-chat-local/platform
platform/persistence/                       @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/backend
platform/security/                          @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/governance

# ── Bootstrap e wiring de runtime (apps/api) ────────────────────────────────
# RACI: Backend R | Platform A
apps/api/src/bootstrap/                     @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/platform
apps/api/src/entrypoints/                   @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/platform
apps/api/src/http/                          @meu-chat-local/backend

# Dockerfile da API: mudanca de runtime afeta platform tambem
apps/api/Dockerfile                         @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/backend

# ── Contratos transversais (shared) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# RACI: Backend R | Platform A | Frontend C
# Mudancas aqui tem impacto em todos os modulos — revisao cruzada obrigatoria
shared/                                     @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/platform
shared/security/                            @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance

# ── Frontend (apps/web e apps/web-admin) ────────────────────────────────────
# RACI: Frontend R/A | Backend C
apps/web/                                   @meu-chat-local/frontend
apps/web-admin/                             @meu-chat-local/frontend @meu-chat-local/backend

# ── Infraestrutura de ops e CI/CD ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Mudancas em docker-compose, scripts e workflows afetam todos — platform e governance
ops/                                        @meu-chat-local/platform
ops/docker/                                 @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/backend
ops/github/workflows/                       @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/governance

# ── Governanca do repositorio (.github) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Qualquer mudanca nos arquivos de governanca exige aprovacao de governance + platform
.github/                                    @meu-chat-local/governance @meu-chat-local/platform
.github/CODEOWNERS                          @meu-chat-local/governance @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/backend
.github/labels.yml                          @meu-chat-local/governance
.github/workflows/                          @meu-chat-local/platform @meu-chat-local/governance

# ── Documentacao arquitetural ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# RACI: qualquer camada pode propor; governance aprova impacto estrutural
README.md                                   @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance
docs/                                       @meu-chat-local/backend @meu-chat-local/governance
CHANGELOG.md                                @meu-chat-local/governance
